Repository Name Unauthorized: Monroe County Library Florida History Department
Notes: This repository holds local government records, court records, 1823-1845, several large scrapbooks containing photographs of Key West and the Keys, genealogical oral histories, land records and some local business materials.The Scott De Wolfe collection contains some of the oldest images of Key West.Many are now in an online gallery as is a Key Name Search  Gazetteer which gives the origins of the names of the Florida Keys
